# By default the server authenticates with DefaultAzureCredential, so it
# will use your current Azure login (for example from `az login`) and none
# of the variables below are required.
#
# Uncomment and fill the variables below only if you want to force a
# specific credential (client secret or certificate) – typically for CI
# scenarios where no interactive login is available.

# --- Client secret authentication (optional) ---
# TENANT_ID=""
# CLIENT_ID=""
# CLIENT_SECRET=""

# --- Certificate authentication (optional) ---
# TENANT_ID=""
# CLIENT_ID=""
# CERTIFICATE_PATH=""
# CERTIFICATE_PWD=""
